      • updateMinMaxTempCache

        public void updateMinMaxTempCache​(double temp)
        Updates the cache for the min and max temperature for a player to reach. This is calculated live due to some factors not being completely known such as armor when loading in the values. THe min and max values are used to determine things such as the boss bars percentage.
        Parameters:
        temp - temperature value to check for a cache update against.
